The '''Zeebrugge Hub''' is the [[natural gas]] [[physical trading point]] in [[Zeebrugge]], [[Belgium]].  It is connected to the [[National Balancing Point (UK)]] via the [[Interconnector (North Sea)|Interconnector]].

